1
00:01:23,844 --> 00:01:30,592
[Weaving A Tale of Love 2]

2
00:01:32,064 --> 00:01:35,840
[Episode 25]

3
00:01:36,499 --> 00:01:40,796
Although you did not be famous overnight
in the battle this time,

4
00:01:41,356 --> 00:01:44,796
you have already seen the gap
between you and others.

5
00:01:47,836 --> 00:01:51,596
A gentleman should constantly strike to become
strong just like the evolution of the universe

6
00:01:52,436 --> 00:01:55,996
and cultivate to become tolerant
just like the earth bears everything on it.

7
00:01:56,596 --> 00:01:58,596
I surely believe in Chongyu.

8
00:01:59,636 --> 00:02:04,476
He will definitely lead Xizhou
to its former glory in the future.

9
00:02:07,396 --> 00:02:11,236
Drink a few more glasses with me tonight.

10
00:02:12,396 --> 00:02:13,836
Drinking is harmful to your health.

11
00:02:14,556 --> 00:02:19,156
So what? Let's go.

12
00:02:19,156 --> 00:02:21,276
Father. Father.

13
00:02:22,636 --> 00:02:23,680
Let's go.

14
00:02:24,192 --> 00:02:25,236
Father.

15
00:02:25,236 --> 00:02:26,636
Have a couple more.

16
00:02:26,636 --> 00:02:28,436
Please don't drag me.

17
00:02:34,076 --> 00:02:35,168
Hurry up.

18
00:02:37,076 --> 00:02:39,336
Minister. Madam.

19
00:02:39,336 --> 00:02:42,136
Each family in the village
has sent their capable daughters.

20
00:02:42,136 --> 00:02:44,816
If Madam needs something, just tell them.

21
00:02:44,816 --> 00:02:46,156
Thank you for your hard work,
Village Mayor Zhou.

22
00:02:46,156 --> 00:02:47,436
You are welcome.

23
00:02:49,996 --> 00:02:52,156
Village Mayor Zhou, please gather all men

24
00:02:52,156 --> 00:02:53,436
to village gate,

25
00:02:54,396 --> 00:02:55,488
Okay,

26
00:02:59,676 --> 00:03:02,876
Yunyi. Minniang.
Take out raw cotton cloth without seeds

27
00:03:02,876 --> 00:03:04,596
and the common cotton cloth made in workshops.

28
00:03:04,596 --> 00:03:05,956
Please pass them around.

29
00:03:05,956 --> 00:03:07,008
Okay.

30
00:03:11,636 --> 00:03:13,196
Look! Take a look quickly.

31
00:03:20,596 --> 00:03:22,376
Madam, what method did you use?

32
00:03:22,376 --> 00:03:25,096
How can this woven cotton cloth be so soft?

33
00:03:25,096 --> 00:03:27,756
How did this raw cotton cloth become so clean?

34
00:03:28,316 --> 00:03:29,756
There's nothing particular.

35
00:03:29,756 --> 00:03:31,556
The cotton cloth that you see

36
00:03:31,556 --> 00:03:33,916
is deseeded and softened by a weaving machine.

37
00:03:33,916 --> 00:03:35,556
As long as this cotton is used,

38
00:03:35,556 --> 00:03:38,296
everyone can weave soft cotton cloth.

39
00:03:38,296 --> 00:03:40,476
Not to mention that it could replace silk
for paying weaving tax.

40
00:03:40,476 --> 00:03:42,076
If take it to the market,

41
00:03:42,076 --> 00:03:43,796
one piece could also be exchanged
for a string of coins.

42
00:03:44,596 --> 00:03:46,356
A string of coins? that's too much.

43
00:03:47,196 --> 00:03:49,036
Senior Official allow us to use cotton.

44
00:03:49,036 --> 00:03:51,756
Everyone knows that it can replace silk
for paying weaving tax.

45
00:03:52,276 --> 00:03:56,156
In Xizhou, everyone knows that cotton is easy
to grow but difficult to be woven.

46
00:03:56,156 --> 00:03:58,676
Just deseeding requires a lot of efforts.

47
00:03:59,276 --> 00:04:02,236
Therefore, it's not because the family
really can't afford cloth.

48
00:04:02,236 --> 00:04:05,456
Normal women would never try this.

49
00:04:05,456 --> 00:04:08,596
But now there's such clean,
soft, and pure cotton.

50
00:04:08,596 --> 00:04:10,476
And it's possible to exchange it
for a string of money.

51
00:04:10,476 --> 00:04:12,156
It truly broadens our horizons.

52
00:04:13,356 --> 00:04:16,696
I wonder
if Madam could possibly show us the method.

53
00:04:16,696 --> 00:04:17,756
Then follow me.

54
00:04:18,916 --> 00:04:20,436
Come on, let's go and have a look.

55
00:04:38,956 --> 00:04:40,836
Now I show it to everyone.

56
00:04:42,156 --> 00:04:45,256
As long as you handle the method,
everyone can learn it.

57
00:04:45,256 --> 00:04:46,556
Please watch carefully.

58
00:05:13,676 --> 00:05:15,516
Snacks in the countryside are not elaborate.

59
00:05:15,516 --> 00:05:17,236
Ladies, please have a little bit.

60
00:05:17,236 --> 00:05:19,216
Thanks for your hardworking.

61
00:05:19,216 --> 00:05:21,236
I will prepare some drinks and dishes outside.

62
00:05:21,236 --> 00:05:23,196
Madam, if you need anything, just tell me.

63
00:05:25,556 --> 00:05:27,516
The pastries here hardly tasty.

64
00:05:27,516 --> 00:05:29,556
Madam, please taste what Minniang has brought.

65
00:05:29,556 --> 00:05:30,876
Is it edible?

66
00:05:50,276 --> 00:05:52,076
Is everything fine
when you distribute errand boys?

67
00:05:52,676 --> 00:05:54,836
Madam's idea is excellent.

68
00:05:55,436 --> 00:05:57,096
If those women had not went there quickly

69
00:05:57,096 --> 00:06:00,036
and strongly praised the cotton
promoted by Madam,

70
00:06:00,036 --> 00:06:03,836
Today's distribution
would not be so successful.

71
00:06:04,436 --> 00:06:06,756
It is Minister that organized well
and did everything by himself.

72
00:06:06,756 --> 00:06:09,396
For promoting in every village and town,
Liuli dare not claim the credit.

73
00:06:14,596 --> 00:06:16,116
Minister has been working hard all day.

74
00:06:16,116 --> 00:06:18,436
Please sit down and have some tea and snacks.

75
00:06:18,436 --> 00:06:20,316
Yes, yes, sit down quickly.

76
00:06:21,356 --> 00:06:22,596
These are all brought by Minniang.

77
00:06:22,596 --> 00:06:24,356
They all are your taste.

78
00:06:25,316 --> 00:06:26,476
Excuse me for a moment.

79
00:06:26,476 --> 00:06:28,316
Go to see how the meal is going.

80
00:06:35,676 --> 00:06:36,836
I heard you coughing continuously.

81
00:06:36,836 --> 00:06:38,256
Your voice is a bit hoarse.

82
00:06:38,256 --> 00:06:39,676
I have added sanguisorba in it.

83
00:06:39,676 --> 00:06:41,796
It can moisturize lungs and relieve cough.
Have it please.

84
00:06:43,556 --> 00:06:45,896
Minister's meals are so exquisite.

85
00:06:45,896 --> 00:06:47,716
He wouldn't eat such crude things,

86
00:06:47,716 --> 00:06:49,556
not to mention such coarse tea sets.

87
00:06:49,556 --> 00:06:51,876
Let alone unknown sanguisorba.

88
00:06:52,396 --> 00:06:54,076
How could it be unknown?

89
00:06:54,076 --> 00:06:56,036
I just dug it up in the courtyard on my own.

90
00:07:00,276 --> 00:07:03,636
Minister trusts me. Sanguisorba is the best
for moisturizing lungs and relieving cough.

91
00:07:05,036 --> 00:07:08,116
Yunyi, stop.
There are many famous doctors around Minister.

92
00:07:08,116 --> 00:07:10,596
For a minor cough,
your folk remedies are not necessary.

93
00:07:11,516 --> 00:07:13,636
But by drinking one or two cups
of Sanguisorba water,

94
00:07:13,636 --> 00:07:14,876
he will get better.

95
00:07:14,876 --> 00:07:16,276
Why do we make it so troublesome?

96
00:07:29,568 --> 00:07:31,636
Minister, you are smart.

97
00:07:31,636 --> 00:07:33,876
After drinking two more cups,
your cough will be cured tomorrow.

98
00:08:01,236 --> 00:08:04,316
Minister agreed to drink the Sanguisorba water
offered by Yunyi.

99
00:08:04,316 --> 00:08:05,756
It surprises me.

100
00:08:06,476 --> 00:08:07,996
Based on my understanding of Minister,

101
00:08:07,996 --> 00:08:11,276
Minister wouldn't touch unknown things.

102
00:08:15,916 --> 00:08:17,356
Perhaps it's a moment of tenderness.

103
00:08:19,316 --> 00:08:21,076
I have also been forced
to drift in foreign lands

104
00:08:21,676 --> 00:08:23,328
but there never has been a moment.

105
00:08:23,328 --> 00:08:26,196
I lived as brightly and simply as she did.

106
00:08:47,756 --> 00:08:50,336
What things happen between sis and Minister?

107
00:08:50,336 --> 00:08:52,076
They avoid us.

108
00:08:53,196 --> 00:08:54,316
How would I know that?

109
00:08:55,876 --> 00:08:58,416
I see Yunyi is very enthusiastic
towards Minister.

110
00:08:58,416 --> 00:09:00,276
Does she love Minister?

111
00:09:02,236 --> 00:09:03,328
Yes.

112
00:09:04,396 --> 00:09:05,408
How could it be possible?

113
00:09:06,476 --> 00:09:07,656
Why not?

114
00:09:07,656 --> 00:09:10,636
Minister is handsome
and cares about the people in Xizhou.

115
00:09:10,636 --> 00:09:11,796
He's a good man.

116
00:09:13,076 --> 00:09:14,356
I mean, how could you

117
00:09:14,356 --> 00:09:17,236
express your feelings so easily.

118
00:09:18,036 --> 00:09:20,876
Liking is simply liking. Why do I cover it up?

119
00:09:21,436 --> 00:09:22,956
What? Do you like him as well?

120
00:09:28,356 --> 00:09:31,036
To tell the truth,
a few years ago, the elders in my family

121
00:09:31,036 --> 00:09:32,796
indeed intended to match me with Minister.

122
00:09:33,636 --> 00:09:37,556
Minister and I
can be considered as childhood sweethearts.

123
00:09:38,956 --> 00:09:40,236
It's a pity.

124
00:09:40,236 --> 00:09:41,836
It's a pity
that Minister doesn't like you, isn't it?

125
00:09:47,196 --> 00:09:49,056
It's not just that Minister doesn't like me.

126
00:09:49,056 --> 00:09:51,636
He doesn't like any girl in this world.

127
00:09:53,836 --> 00:09:55,996
Even if Minister is excellent in all fields,

128
00:09:55,996 --> 00:09:58,596
but he simply loves handsome youths.

129
00:10:01,036 --> 00:10:02,396
Is that really true?

130
00:10:02,396 --> 00:10:05,836
Of course.
Minister has already passed the age of thirty.

131
00:10:05,836 --> 00:10:07,336
Considering his status and position,

132
00:10:07,336 --> 00:10:09,676
have you ever seen any other women by his side?

133
00:10:29,836 --> 00:10:32,876
On Winter Solstice, as vital as the New Year,
my lady herself is going out to shop.

134
00:10:33,516 --> 00:10:34,956
I also wanted to be out for a walk

135
00:10:34,956 --> 00:10:37,076
and see the current situation
of the people in Xizhou.

136
00:10:43,196 --> 00:10:45,276
Madam, here comes a a visitor.

137
00:10:45,276 --> 00:10:46,716
He mentioned
that he brings a message from Master.

138
00:10:46,716 --> 00:10:48,276
I was just about to go out
to look for you, Madam.

139
00:10:48,276 --> 00:10:49,636
Why is he so hurry?

140
00:10:49,636 --> 00:10:51,276
You have to come all the way here yourself.

141
00:10:51,276 --> 00:10:54,596
It's Mi Dalang who sent Yunyi back last time

142
00:10:55,116 --> 00:10:56,976
He said that something happened
at the military camp.

143
00:10:56,976 --> 00:10:59,796
Master sent him to Xizhou
to find Minister Qu to report to the dynasty.

144
00:10:59,796 --> 00:11:00,916
To report to the dynasty?

145
00:11:03,396 --> 00:11:05,716
Tan, please hurry to
Protector-General's Mansion for the Minister.

146
00:11:06,356 --> 00:11:07,392
Yes.

147
00:11:09,156 --> 00:11:11,276
My lady, that Mi Dalang.

148
00:11:11,276 --> 00:11:13,496
His physical condition seems not so good.

149
00:11:13,496 --> 00:11:16,336
I wonder if we need to invite Physician Han.

150
00:11:16,336 --> 00:11:17,696
Let him come over and have a look.

151
00:11:17,696 --> 00:11:18,752
Okay

152
00:11:23,684 --> 00:11:27,588
[Lan Ruo]

153
00:11:37,636 --> 00:11:39,008
Lady Kudi.

154
00:11:39,008 --> 00:11:41,756
Just now,
a person with bloodstains entered your house.

155
00:11:41,756 --> 00:11:44,076
He seems to be the trafficker, Master Mi.

156
00:11:44,076 --> 00:11:45,336
He is not a good person.

157
00:11:45,336 --> 00:11:47,796
Do you need us to go to the Mansion
to ask for some officers?

158
00:11:47,796 --> 00:11:49,696
Thank you everybody, I have heard it.

159
00:11:49,696 --> 00:11:52,256
No need to bother officers.
I know how to handle this.

160
00:11:52,256 --> 00:11:53,280
Well.

161
00:11:54,596 --> 00:11:55,680
Lady Kudi.

162
00:11:59,116 --> 00:12:02,016
Stop talking nonsense about saving people
and sending messages.

163
00:12:02,016 --> 00:12:03,956
[Rising Sun and Forever Moon]
Take a look of yourself.

164
00:12:03,956 --> 00:12:05,756
I can't believe you play tricks on me.

165
00:12:05,756 --> 00:12:06,848
Yunyi.

166
00:12:09,036 --> 00:12:10,196
You go back to your own yard.

167
00:12:10,796 --> 00:12:12,476
I'll handle these matters.

168
00:12:14,196 --> 00:12:15,196
You all can stand down.

169
00:12:15,196 --> 00:12:16,224
Yes.

170
00:12:21,916 --> 00:12:22,996
[Floating Water Workshop]
What on earth has happened?

171
00:12:23,756 --> 00:12:26,516
Sister, don't listen to him.
He is such a devious guy.

172
00:12:26,516 --> 00:12:28,476
Now he fabricates nonsense again,

173
00:12:28,476 --> 00:12:30,876
saying that the Tang army
massacred merchants in Dadu City.

174
00:12:30,876 --> 00:12:33,056
He injured two Tang soldiers
while saving people.

175
00:12:33,056 --> 00:12:35,936
After escaping from the Tang camp,
his brother-in-law asked him to find Minister.

176
00:12:35,936 --> 00:12:37,996
He said to report this to the imperial court.

177
00:12:37,996 --> 00:12:41,116
He does not think about the big city like Dadu.

178
00:12:41,116 --> 00:12:42,716
It's not Helu's territory anyway.

179
00:12:42,716 --> 00:12:44,896
Why would the Tang army massacre the merchants
for no reason?

180
00:12:44,896 --> 00:12:46,316
Totally lie.

181
00:12:47,756 --> 00:12:48,796
Massacre the merchants?

182
00:12:52,316 --> 00:12:54,136
Although I am certainly not such kind person,

183
00:12:54,136 --> 00:12:55,516
what I said today is true.

184
00:12:55,516 --> 00:12:58,936
If I cheat, I will be killed by thunder.

185
00:12:58,936 --> 00:13:00,756
Don't you think
you will not be killed by thunder?

186
00:13:04,556 --> 00:13:06,976
Yunyi, go back to your own courtyard first.

187
00:13:06,976 --> 00:13:09,916
No, sister, he is truly not a good person.

188
00:13:09,916 --> 00:13:11,876
Put the question
whether he is good or not aside.

189
00:13:11,876 --> 00:13:14,516
What he said today is likely to be true.

190
00:13:23,196 --> 00:13:24,256
Thank you, my lady.

191
00:13:25,596 --> 00:13:27,556
I'm grateful to you
for believing in me, my lady.

192
00:13:28,396 --> 00:13:30,756
My lady, you must hurry to summon Minister,
otherwise it will be too late.

193
00:13:31,676 --> 00:13:34,296
General Su said
that massacring the merchants is being a theft.

194
00:13:34,296 --> 00:13:36,676
And I am unwilling to tarnish my reputation
by sharing their loot.

195
00:13:37,236 --> 00:13:39,956
They falsely accused me,
regarding me as the remnants of a city rebel.

196
00:13:40,676 --> 00:13:42,756
Senior Official Pei said
the court must be informed about this.

197
00:13:42,756 --> 00:13:43,836
And the sooner, the better.

198
00:13:46,356 --> 00:13:47,876
I've already sent someone to summon Minister.

199
00:13:48,716 --> 00:13:50,476
Master Mi, please comes in.

200
00:14:04,236 --> 00:14:05,976
I was born to be a bad person.

201
00:14:05,976 --> 00:14:08,956
I entered the city with bad plans this time.

202
00:14:09,916 --> 00:14:12,656
I intended to steal armor
and go to someone's home I know.

203
00:14:12,656 --> 00:14:13,676
To swindle some silver.

204
00:14:15,396 --> 00:14:16,436
But who knew

205
00:14:43,676 --> 00:14:44,956
that household with dozens of family members

206
00:14:45,756 --> 00:14:47,996
was only a teenage girl left,

207
00:14:48,716 --> 00:14:49,916
Trembling in a water jar.

208
00:14:51,556 --> 00:14:54,836
Recognizing me at a glance,
she burst into tears while hugging my neck.

209
00:15:00,516 --> 00:15:02,916
I then hit two Tang soldiers
who came in after hearing noise.

210
00:15:04,316 --> 00:15:06,196
I sent her out of the city
and helped her onto a horse.

211
00:15:08,876 --> 00:15:10,276
It's all because of me
that I didn't consider things thoroughly.

212
00:15:10,956 --> 00:15:12,276
I brought trouble for General Su.

213
00:15:12,956 --> 00:15:16,396
On the third day,
General Su sent me out of the military camp.

214
00:15:16,916 --> 00:15:20,156
I later heard that General Su refused to accept

215
00:15:20,876 --> 00:15:23,676
gold and silver treasures
scraped from Dadu City

216
00:15:24,476 --> 00:15:27,116
That Deputy Director Wang insisted

217
00:15:27,756 --> 00:15:29,356
I am a scout from Dadu City.

218
00:15:30,236 --> 00:15:32,916
He also said
that General Su has sheltered scouts

219
00:15:33,556 --> 00:15:35,676
so that he showed mercy towards city rebels.

220
00:15:37,076 --> 00:15:39,836
I barely managed to escape
to Senior Official Pei.

221
00:15:41,396 --> 00:15:44,316
Now that it has come to this, the only way is
that we report it to the court.

222
00:15:44,956 --> 00:15:46,236
Let His Majesty be informed of this matter.

223
00:15:46,996 --> 00:15:50,236
It would be best to have Minister Qu,
Protector-General Qu, submit a report.

224
00:15:51,916 --> 00:15:52,992
If that doesn't work,

225
00:15:53,676 --> 00:15:56,196
you could ask Minister to secretly send someone
to take you to Chang'an.

226
00:15:56,196 --> 00:15:57,796
My lady will know

227
00:15:58,996 --> 00:16:00,876
how to make this matter be heard
by the Emperor.

228
00:16:07,076 --> 00:16:08,996
How is the situation
at the military warehouse now?

229
00:16:09,636 --> 00:16:12,436
The military warehouse of the Chief Historian
has no grain left to send.

230
00:16:14,716 --> 00:16:16,356
Since half a month ago,

231
00:16:17,076 --> 00:16:18,796
soldiers' food has already been halved.

232
00:16:20,236 --> 00:16:22,436
The feed for the horses
has been reduced even more.

233
00:16:23,116 --> 00:16:25,096
The warhorses
barely have forage to fill their bellies.

234
00:16:25,096 --> 00:16:27,636
But the private horses used for transportation
by the foot soldiers

235
00:16:28,636 --> 00:16:30,516
are dying in large numbers from hunger.

236
00:16:31,556 --> 00:16:32,716
There is much complaining among the soldiers.

237
00:16:33,236 --> 00:16:35,356
Wang Wendu must have massacred the merchants
in the city.

238
00:16:35,876 --> 00:16:37,636
Aside from returning without nothing,

239
00:16:38,196 --> 00:16:41,436
he loots food, grass, cash and silk
to stabilize the military's morale.

240
00:16:58,756 --> 00:17:00,696
Master Mi, this is Physician Han.

241
00:17:00,696 --> 00:17:03,316
It's better to cure your wounds first
before reporting to Minister.

242
00:17:10,076 --> 00:17:11,104
Thank you, my lady.

243
00:17:12,076 --> 00:17:13,396
I am fine.

244
00:17:13,916 --> 00:17:15,936
I just fell off from horse and broke my nose
in the middle of the night.

245
00:17:15,936 --> 00:17:17,236
Just lost a bit more blood.

246
00:17:20,596 --> 00:17:21,636
Indeed, I am fine.

247
00:17:23,476 --> 00:17:27,596
I just haven't had rest for a few days,
and the bleeding wouldn't stop after the shock.

248
00:17:28,716 --> 00:17:30,036
There are other injuries.

249
00:17:31,876 --> 00:17:35,316
Staying up like this for another two days
would only shorten my life by two years.

250
00:17:44,156 --> 00:17:45,316
Madam, please step aside for a moment.

251
00:17:45,916 --> 00:17:47,876
I need to check his wounds.

252
00:17:49,476 --> 00:17:50,496
Thanks.

253
00:18:01,220 --> 00:18:04,864
[Rising Sun and Forever Moon]

254
00:18:36,416 --> 00:18:38,628
[Protector-General of Xizhou, Qu Zhizhan]

255
00:18:43,076 --> 00:18:45,556
My lady, why are you looking at this?

256
00:18:46,116 --> 00:18:47,796
Could there be some tricks?

257
00:18:48,836 --> 00:18:50,236
Come help me take a look at this.

258
00:18:54,276 --> 00:18:56,596
This one and the other
that maid brought back from An Family

259
00:18:56,596 --> 00:18:59,036
are indeed a bit different.
It's newly issued this year.

260
00:18:59,556 --> 00:19:01,876
This is a masterpiece
into which I've put a night's effort.

261
00:19:04,956 --> 00:19:07,436
It seems
Senior Official Pei must be in danger now.

262
00:19:07,436 --> 00:19:09,156
Advisor Su hated Senior Official Pei.

263
00:19:09,156 --> 00:19:10,916
Senior Official Pei
is bound to have a hard time in the military.

264
00:19:13,596 --> 00:19:15,036
With this fake clearance document,

265
00:19:15,036 --> 00:19:17,436
I can ask Gu to take the An family's servants.

266
00:19:18,236 --> 00:19:20,576
With the help of the An family's
financial power and horses along the way

267
00:19:20,576 --> 00:19:23,596
they arrive at the military
under the pretext of delivering supplies.

268
00:19:24,396 --> 00:19:27,396
To help for Senior Official Pei outside
to prevent persecution from Advisor Su.

269
00:19:31,356 --> 00:19:34,036
The young servant that the lady sent
to wait at the city gate has returned.

270
00:19:34,036 --> 00:19:35,676
He says the Minister has returned.

271
00:19:36,636 --> 00:19:39,596
However,
that child couldn't even get close to Minister.

272
00:19:40,156 --> 00:19:43,076
He said Minister was accompanied
by dozens of people in armor.

273
00:19:43,076 --> 00:19:44,356
They enter the city gate together.

274
00:19:44,956 --> 00:19:46,576
Those people all looked hostile.

275
00:19:46,576 --> 00:19:49,256
Our young servant approached them
but hadn't even spoken one word yet.

276
00:19:49,256 --> 00:19:50,896
He was pushed aside.

277
00:19:50,896 --> 00:19:52,856
However, that child was quite clever.

278
00:19:52,856 --> 00:19:55,636
He noticed that an attendant of Minister
was lagging behind.

279
00:19:55,636 --> 00:19:57,936
So he went up and said a few words.

280
00:19:57,936 --> 00:20:02,116
The attendant replied
that he would report to Minister when free.

281
00:20:03,636 --> 00:20:05,396
Dozens of people in armor.

282
00:20:05,396 --> 00:20:07,316
Do you find out who these people are?

283
00:20:07,956 --> 00:20:11,276
They said that the leader
is the military advisor Su Nanjin.

284
00:20:17,436 --> 00:20:18,676
[Peace and Safe Spread Far]
Is what you said true?

285
00:20:19,556 --> 00:20:20,956
The army has already returned.

286
00:20:20,956 --> 00:20:24,956
T-That Senior Official Pei
was already detained by the army.

287
00:20:24,956 --> 00:20:27,236
How dare I speak nonsense
about this vital matter?

288
00:20:28,396 --> 00:20:30,556
If this Pei Xingjian is just ineffective
in dispatching military provisions,

289
00:20:30,556 --> 00:20:31,904
then let it be.

290
00:20:31,904 --> 00:20:35,076
He also sided with Su Dingfang in showing mercy
to the scouts from Dadu City.

291
00:20:35,076 --> 00:20:37,356
How could the Deputy Director Wang
tolerate him?

292
00:20:38,236 --> 00:20:41,636
Logically speaking, Pei Xingjian
is an official of Xizhou after all.

293
00:20:42,196 --> 00:20:44,276
It should be Protector-General Qu
to decide his fate.

294
00:20:45,036 --> 00:20:46,956
Deputy Director Wang
wants me to inform the Protector-General.

295
00:20:47,836 --> 00:20:50,916
In a few days,
Pei Xingjian will be escorted back to Xizhou.

296
00:20:52,396 --> 00:20:53,440
Dadu.

297
00:20:54,556 --> 00:20:57,156
Is Master Su referring to the Dadu City
on the west of Yingsuochuan Valley?

298
00:20:58,716 --> 00:21:01,276
I believe
this city is quite affluent as far as I know.

299
00:21:01,996 --> 00:21:03,576
The lord of the city is a sly character.

300
00:21:03,576 --> 00:21:05,516
It seems to have the guts

301
00:21:06,076 --> 00:21:07,956
to place a spy in the Tang army.

302
00:21:08,756 --> 00:21:10,756
Is he totally unaware of the danger?

303
00:21:10,756 --> 00:21:11,756
Isn't that the truth?

304
00:21:13,996 --> 00:21:15,356
Deputy Director Wang originally wanted to

305
00:21:15,356 --> 00:21:17,376
let Su Dingfang have dignity.

306
00:21:17,376 --> 00:21:18,996
But he took advantage
of his previous military exploits,

307
00:21:18,996 --> 00:21:20,716
unfairly protecting the spy from Dadu City.

308
00:21:21,316 --> 00:21:23,156
He even secretly let him out of camp.

309
00:21:23,836 --> 00:21:25,196
Now, this spy from Dadu city

310
00:21:25,196 --> 00:21:27,156
has reached Xizhou probably.

311
00:21:28,476 --> 00:21:30,716
Deputy Director Wang has asked me
to cooperate with Protector-General Qu

312
00:21:30,716 --> 00:21:32,196
to catch this spy from Dadu.

313
00:21:32,836 --> 00:21:35,436
What's your opinion, Protector-General Qu?

314
00:21:43,116 --> 00:21:47,556
Since Deputy Director Wang has ordered,
I must obey.

315
00:21:49,396 --> 00:21:51,956
I heard from Chongyu that soldiers and horses
who have joined the army

316
00:21:51,956 --> 00:21:54,076
have secured the city gate of Xizhou.

317
00:21:54,756 --> 00:21:56,556
I suspect that the spy cannot escape anymore.

318
00:21:57,156 --> 00:22:00,356
The Advisor has been through many hardships
along the way.

319
00:22:00,356 --> 00:22:04,156
Do you need to freshen up
and rest for a moment?

320
00:22:04,156 --> 00:22:05,436
Military affairs matter.

321
00:22:06,756 --> 00:22:09,436
The spy is likely hiding
in Pei Xingjian's house.

322
00:22:10,356 --> 00:22:14,216
We should capture him immediately
to avoid more complications.

323
00:22:14,216 --> 00:22:15,516
Master Su, don't worry.

324
00:22:16,356 --> 00:22:19,976
I will arrange people
to spot Pei Xingjian's house secretly.

325
00:22:19,976 --> 00:22:23,016
By the way, find out the situation there
these past few days.

326
00:22:23,016 --> 00:22:26,036
If there is any news,
I'll inform you immediately

327
00:22:28,356 --> 00:22:30,956
If so, thanks for Chongyu.

328
00:22:39,796 --> 00:22:42,316
Chongyu, don't blame me.
I don't mean to concealed it from you.

329
00:22:43,356 --> 00:22:44,856
It's just
that I accept military orders this time.

330
00:22:44,856 --> 00:22:47,156
I can't reveal the news until we get to Xizhou.

331
00:22:47,876 --> 00:22:49,676
I wondered why Ziyu said so

332
00:22:49,676 --> 00:22:51,996
and asked me
who else is in the Pei Shouyue's family.

333
00:22:52,836 --> 00:22:55,196
You'd better pay more attention
to catching the spy.

334
00:22:55,196 --> 00:22:57,716
[Qu's Mansion]
Thoroughly inspect the merchants heading east.

335
00:22:57,716 --> 00:22:59,116
Do not let them exploit any loopholes.

336
00:23:00,556 --> 00:23:02,316
As long as we catch them red-handed this time,

337
00:23:02,876 --> 00:23:05,796
This Pei Shouyue will definitely not
escape from punishment.

338
00:23:05,796 --> 00:23:08,116
Ziyu, don't worry. I totally understand.

339
00:23:17,252 --> 00:23:19,104
[Qu's Mansion]

340
00:23:23,680 --> 00:23:24,768
Minister.

341
00:23:24,768 --> 00:23:25,856
What's the matter?

342
00:23:25,856 --> 00:23:27,236
The wife of Senior Official Pei
has sent someone to look for you.

343
00:23:27,236 --> 00:23:28,716
Please visit Floating Water Workshop
as soon as possible.

344
00:23:30,556 --> 00:23:31,616
Okay.

345
00:23:40,436 --> 00:23:43,236
Madam, I have already change drug dressing
for Master Mi.

346
00:23:43,236 --> 00:23:46,356
He will recover after resting for two days.
Madam, please do not worry.

347
00:23:47,156 --> 00:23:48,236
Thank you, Physician Han.

348
00:23:49,436 --> 00:23:52,156
I must the matter of life and death to you.

349
00:23:53,276 --> 00:23:54,636
Please ask me as your will, Madam.

350
00:23:55,276 --> 00:23:58,356
I wonder
if Physician Han could make Mr. Mi's injuries

351
00:23:58,356 --> 00:24:00,716
appear more critical.

352
00:24:00,716 --> 00:24:03,356
It's best to look like
he is on the brink of death.

353
00:24:06,076 --> 00:24:07,996
Merchants in Dadu City have been murdered.

354
00:24:07,996 --> 00:24:10,456
Master Mi. was falsely accused
of being a spy in Dadu.

355
00:24:10,456 --> 00:24:12,116
I have already asked Ni to tell you.

356
00:24:13,076 --> 00:24:16,816
If he is caught and sent to the army,
it's certain that he won't come back.

357
00:24:16,816 --> 00:24:18,836
Even Senior Official Pei will be accused.

358
00:24:19,436 --> 00:24:21,876
I have thought of a risky plan.

359
00:24:22,556 --> 00:24:25,476
The more miserable Mi Dalang's appearance,
the better.

360
00:24:26,956 --> 00:24:28,596
I am going to fake the wound right away.

361
00:24:28,596 --> 00:24:29,632
Thank you.

362
00:24:36,516 --> 00:24:41,156
Madam, I have a more convenient drug.

363
00:24:42,996 --> 00:24:45,316
I wonder if Madam is willing to try it.

364
00:24:47,636 --> 00:24:49,716
Alright, you prepare first.

365
00:24:49,716 --> 00:24:51,356
Just follow my arrangements later.

366
00:25:02,396 --> 00:25:04,196
Father,
there must be something strange about this.

367
00:25:04,716 --> 00:25:06,976
Pei Xingjian and Su Dingfang are not someone
who does not know what matters.

368
00:25:06,976 --> 00:25:08,236
How could it happen without reason?

369
00:25:08,236 --> 00:25:09,836
To cover up for some sort of spy.

370
00:25:13,836 --> 00:25:14,912
Go on.

371
00:25:15,876 --> 00:25:19,036
Send someone to give a message
to Pei's mansion.

372
00:25:21,036 --> 00:25:24,316
Senior Official Pei and his wife
are our benefactors.

373
00:25:25,636 --> 00:25:27,516
They are also benefactors of the people
in Xizhou.

374
00:25:31,636 --> 00:25:32,672
Help him.

375
00:25:39,956 --> 00:25:41,056
Why is it so greasy?

376
00:25:41,756 --> 00:25:44,396
Tell the kitchen to cut off all the meat
for my father next two days.

377
00:25:44,396 --> 00:25:45,504
Just cut it all off

378
00:25:47,596 --> 00:25:49,596
Naughty boy. How could I live without meat?

379
00:25:55,972 --> 00:25:57,316
[Settled in Taishan]

380
00:25:57,316 --> 00:25:58,336
Madam.

381
00:25:59,676 --> 00:26:01,556
I already know why Madam has invited me here.

382
00:26:01,556 --> 00:26:03,696
I came just to inform Madam.

383
00:26:03,696 --> 00:26:06,096
Mr. Su has already taken orders
from the Chief Administrator

384
00:26:06,096 --> 00:26:08,276
to investigate the Dadu spy in Xizhou.

385
00:26:08,276 --> 00:26:10,616
Later,
I will lead people to patrol the whole city.

386
00:26:10,616 --> 00:26:12,396
Madam need to make some preparations please.

387
00:26:13,236 --> 00:26:14,696
I assume that Minister is not aware

388
00:26:14,696 --> 00:26:16,836
what on earth has happened inside Dadu City.

389
00:26:21,036 --> 00:26:22,436
What's the matter?

390
00:26:22,436 --> 00:26:24,596
Master Mi,
please come out to greet the Minister.

391
00:26:33,316 --> 00:26:34,400
Minister.

392
00:26:35,716 --> 00:26:36,800
Master Mi.

393
00:26:37,516 --> 00:26:41,756
Minister, the merchants inside Dadu City
have been slaughtered.

394
00:26:43,396 --> 00:26:44,836
What did you say?

395
00:26:44,836 --> 00:26:48,576
General Su Dingfang refuses
to collude with Deputy Director Wang.

396
00:26:48,576 --> 00:26:49,836
Then Deputy Director Wang slandered him

397
00:26:49,836 --> 00:26:51,596
that he helped me who is a spy from Dadu.

398
00:26:52,996 --> 00:26:56,136
Minister, you know someone named.

399
00:26:56,136 --> 00:26:58,256
I was born and raised in the Xizhou.

400
00:26:58,256 --> 00:26:59,556
How dare I do that

401
00:26:59,556 --> 00:27:02,304
stupid spy of Dadu? Minister.

402
00:27:08,316 --> 00:27:09,376
Did you say

403
00:27:10,916 --> 00:27:13,036
the merchants in Dadu City

404
00:27:16,796 --> 00:27:18,076
were all slaughtered?

405
00:27:21,196 --> 00:27:24,676
Minister, as Senior Official said,
things have happened.

406
00:27:25,236 --> 00:27:27,976
Only you
can vindicate innocent people of Dadu City.

407
00:27:27,976 --> 00:27:30,296
Protector-General Qu please report it
to the imperial court.

408
00:27:30,296 --> 00:27:33,316
Inform His Majesty of this deep grievance
as soon as possible.

409
00:27:33,836 --> 00:27:36,956
Convict those executioners, Minister.

410
00:27:59,516 --> 00:28:01,276
My Qu family is located
in the remote southwest frontier.

411
00:28:02,796 --> 00:28:04,176
We lack influence and are weak in power.

412
00:28:04,176 --> 00:28:08,116
If we overtly confront General Su, I'm afraid…

413
00:28:17,276 --> 00:28:18,836
I do have a safe and reliable method.

414
00:28:21,316 --> 00:28:22,856
Minister, you must be aware as well.

415
00:28:22,856 --> 00:28:25,996
I received help from Madam Rongguo,
the Empress's mother.

416
00:28:25,996 --> 00:28:28,196
Madam Rongguo
has been exceptionally kind to Liuli.

417
00:28:29,516 --> 00:28:33,136
I ask Minister to secretly send an officer
to deliver a message to Chang'an for me.

418
00:28:33,136 --> 00:28:36,396
Liuli guarantees
that no matter how this matter is resolved,

419
00:28:36,396 --> 00:28:38,276
it will not implicate the family of the Qu.

420
00:28:38,276 --> 00:28:40,436
Furthermore, it might even make it possible for

421
00:28:40,436 --> 00:28:43,236
the Empress to be aware of Minister's loyalty.

422
00:28:50,356 --> 00:28:53,516
As for loyalty or not,
there is no need to mention it now.

423
00:28:54,796 --> 00:28:57,596
I, on the other hand,
would like to see these utterly mad men.

424
00:28:59,156 --> 00:29:00,956
I wonder what kind of fate will they meet.

425
00:29:04,436 --> 00:29:07,036
Madam, if there is any letter
to be sent to Chang'an

426
00:29:07,556 --> 00:29:10,396
Chongyu is willing to do for you
with whole heart.

427
00:29:39,156 --> 00:29:40,192
Thank you very much, Minister.

428
00:29:40,876 --> 00:29:42,876
This is the Ruyi that the Empress awarded me

429
00:29:42,876 --> 00:29:44,556
and the letter I wrote to the Empress

430
00:29:45,276 --> 00:29:46,996
When Minister's servants
have arrived at the Duke's mansion,

431
00:29:46,996 --> 00:29:48,276
they Just give the word

432
00:29:48,276 --> 00:29:50,716
that 'The Kudi clan sent someone
to greet to Madam Rongguo'.

433
00:29:50,716 --> 00:29:52,076
Someone will probably report it.

434
00:29:53,076 --> 00:29:56,716
Does the lady trust me so much?

435
00:29:58,116 --> 00:30:01,316
Minister has pride,
and he would surely not feed the dragon.

436
00:30:01,316 --> 00:30:04,816
Furthermore, this matter will sooner or later
become known to the world

437
00:30:04,816 --> 00:30:07,396
There is no need for Minister stain his fame
by associating with the corrupt.

438
00:30:11,676 --> 00:30:14,316
This letter will surely be delivered
by Chongyu.

439
00:30:15,156 --> 00:30:17,636
It's just that the city gates are now closed.

440
00:30:19,116 --> 00:30:22,116
Madam, what will you do with Master Mi.?

441
00:30:24,876 --> 00:30:25,996
You don't need to worry.

442
00:30:31,492 --> 00:30:36,576
[For the Benefit of the People]

443
00:30:44,964 --> 00:30:46,464
[Qu's Residence]

444
00:30:51,844 --> 00:30:54,432
[A Thousand Rooms of Resounding Strings]

445
00:30:54,432 --> 00:30:57,996
How are things going?
Have you caught that Dadu scout?

446
00:30:59,196 --> 00:31:01,156
Mr. Su,
you've been keeping me in such suspense.

447
00:31:02,396 --> 00:31:05,316
I just went to the Pei Family,
but I didn't see the Dadu scout.

448
00:31:05,316 --> 00:31:07,416
I only saw one man selling live stocks.

449
00:31:07,416 --> 00:31:10,396
The merchant from Xizhou, Master Mi,
was beaten until he was almost breathless.

450
00:31:10,396 --> 00:31:11,896
But he was still there, shouting and yelling,

451
00:31:11,896 --> 00:31:14,236
that the merchants were all slaughtered.
Everyone is dead.

452
00:31:14,236 --> 00:31:16,836
The treasure has been stolen,
and now they want to kill him.

453
00:31:17,556 --> 00:31:19,456
Why didn't Chongyu bring him back?

454
00:31:19,456 --> 00:31:21,156
Nut allow him to babble nonsense there.

455
00:31:21,156 --> 00:31:22,240
Bring him back?

456
00:31:24,196 --> 00:31:25,248
Easier said than done.

457
00:31:27,036 --> 00:31:30,016
Given such event,
the Kudi family did not only invite a doctor

458
00:31:30,016 --> 00:31:31,696
but also invited a mage to cast spells.

459
00:31:31,696 --> 00:31:33,676
Now Pei family's crowded outside the door.

460
00:31:33,676 --> 00:31:35,736
Everyone comes to see Master Mi
who has been bewitched.

461
00:31:35,736 --> 00:31:37,996
Originally, Master Mi was a tyrant in Xizhou,
committing numerous misdeeds.

462
00:31:37,996 --> 00:31:42,096
Therefore, everyone is clapping and cheering,
saying he was deserved to be bewitched.

463
00:31:42,096 --> 00:31:44,276
I actually want to say this in public.

464
00:31:44,276 --> 00:31:45,996
This person is indeed a spy form Dadu.

465
00:31:48,196 --> 00:31:49,476
But I can't say it out.

466
00:32:00,276 --> 00:32:02,276
How is Dadu now?

467
00:32:04,556 --> 00:32:07,196
Have those merchants
really been slaughtered to the last man?

468
00:32:11,116 --> 00:32:12,236
Well, some people were indeed killed.

469
00:32:17,796 --> 00:32:20,076
They resist stubbornly.

470
00:32:37,076 --> 00:32:39,196
Minister. Minister.

471
00:33:16,556 --> 00:33:20,116
Minister,
isn't this just a case of the poor dying?

472
00:33:24,236 --> 00:33:26,196
You didn't believe
that bully's nonsense, did you?

473
00:33:26,196 --> 00:33:27,996
Instead,
you suspect Chief Administrator and me.

474
00:33:32,636 --> 00:33:36,796
You also don't want to obey
the Chief Administrator's military orders.

475
00:33:39,156 --> 00:33:42,716
Master Mi. is now
in the courtyard of the Pei family.

476
00:33:43,796 --> 00:33:47,476
If you wish, my Lord,
you could capture him at any time.

477
00:33:49,076 --> 00:33:53,236
Let the people of Xizhou know
that this person is not possessed.

478
00:33:54,836 --> 00:33:56,956
It turns out
that the Chief Administrator is truly greedy.

479
00:33:58,876 --> 00:34:00,676
He butchered the steadfast merchant.

480
00:34:01,876 --> 00:34:06,076
So you really wanted to kill them to death.

481
00:34:13,236 --> 00:34:14,276
Ziyu, please figure it out.

482
00:34:15,756 --> 00:34:17,316
Chongyu is much different from you.

483
00:34:18,396 --> 00:34:21,516
Qu family has been living in Xizhou
for generations.

484
00:34:22,156 --> 00:34:26,516
I can't disregard the reputation
of my Qu family.

485
00:34:28,196 --> 00:34:31,236
Sorry, I can't interfere in this matter.

486
00:34:33,436 --> 00:34:34,496
Please, do as you wish.

487
00:34:48,900 --> 00:34:52,096
[For the Benefit of the People]

488
00:34:52,772 --> 00:34:54,752
[A Thousand Rooms of Resounding Strings]

489
00:34:58,596 --> 00:35:01,024
[Qu's Residence]

490
00:35:15,316 --> 00:35:16,916
Now the elderly ladies have taken a look at it.

491
00:35:16,916 --> 00:35:19,396
Could you please check if
Master Mi has been better?

492
00:35:44,716 --> 00:35:47,796
Madam, Master Mi's condition is getting worse.

493
00:35:48,516 --> 00:35:50,916
Please decide early, Madam.

494
00:35:50,916 --> 00:35:52,756
Since he has begged for seeing Senior Official.

495
00:35:52,756 --> 00:35:56,236
Although I cannot save him,
I just can't abandon him.

496
00:35:56,236 --> 00:35:58,916
Madam, I will take Master Mi to my place.

497
00:35:58,916 --> 00:36:03,116
If I can save him, I will;
if not, I'll accompany him on his last journey.

498
00:36:03,876 --> 00:36:04,960
Much thanks to Physician Han.

499
00:36:22,196 --> 00:36:26,836
The city has been slaughtered,
all the gold and silver have been looted.

500
00:36:27,356 --> 00:36:29,876
They-They want to kill people to death.

501
00:36:32,916 --> 00:36:34,176
Everyone gets out of the way for me.

502
00:36:34,176 --> 00:36:35,276
Move, move, move aside.

503
00:36:35,916 --> 00:36:37,036
The city has been massacred.

504
00:36:37,596 --> 00:36:38,756
Hurry up and make him shut up.

505
00:36:39,396 --> 00:36:40,996
Such babbling is nonsensical.

506
00:36:42,356 --> 00:36:45,236
Who's the doctor? Quickly shut him up.

507
00:36:45,236 --> 00:36:47,816
If he dares to spout another nonsensical word…

508
00:36:47,816 --> 00:36:48,928
And what of it?

509
00:36:50,996 --> 00:36:54,156
Madam, I didn't find you were here.
Sorry for offending you.

510
00:36:54,756 --> 00:36:55,808
I am helpless as well.

511
00:36:56,996 --> 00:36:58,596
This Mr. Mi was struggling the other day.

512
00:36:58,596 --> 00:37:01,056
And fall upon when entering my courtyard.

513
00:37:01,056 --> 00:37:02,936
I've called for a doctor for two days in a row.

514
00:37:02,936 --> 00:37:05,136
Unfortunately,
not only has he not regained consciousness.

515
00:37:05,136 --> 00:37:06,636
But he started to talk nonsense instead.

516
00:37:07,356 --> 00:37:08,876
I also want him to calm down.

517
00:37:08,876 --> 00:37:12,356
But the doctor said
that Master Mi's injuries were too severe.

518
00:37:12,356 --> 00:37:15,016
If give him more medicine,
he might not be able to bear it.

519
00:37:15,016 --> 00:37:16,356
But if the medicine is not used,

520
00:37:16,356 --> 00:37:18,956
he can't keep yelling like this for long.

521
00:37:21,516 --> 00:37:24,116
Have you come here
for any official matters today?

522
00:37:24,116 --> 00:37:25,716
Madam.

523
00:37:25,716 --> 00:37:28,356
It was said that Master Mi forced good people
into bad one.

524
00:37:28,356 --> 00:37:31,436
They want to take him to reply, madam.

525
00:37:32,636 --> 00:37:35,636
You all have also seen Master Mi's situation.

526
00:37:36,196 --> 00:37:37,756
Does he seem to be able to respond?

527
00:37:39,676 --> 00:37:40,916
Move aside, move aside, move aside,

528
00:37:45,280 --> 00:37:47,596
Advisor Su, how do you think what we should do?

529
00:37:53,076 --> 00:37:56,716
Madam Kudi, long time no see.

530
00:37:58,036 --> 00:37:59,104
Master Su.

531
00:38:01,756 --> 00:38:03,596
I suppose he must be Master Mi.

532
00:38:04,476 --> 00:38:08,196
You allow him to talk nonsense
and stir up people's hearts here?

533
00:38:10,196 --> 00:38:12,476
This man, Mi Dalang, has committed

534
00:38:12,476 --> 00:38:13,716
coercing the innocent into degrading acts
several times in Yizhou.

535
00:38:14,396 --> 00:38:16,116
I'll take him back for questioning.

536
00:38:16,836 --> 00:38:18,676
Hope that you can do me a favor.

537
00:38:20,156 --> 00:38:21,344
Master Su.

538
00:38:21,344 --> 00:38:24,580
Look at him. Can he bear such turbulence?

539
00:38:25,316 --> 00:38:28,856
Could you please show mercy to him
and allow him to have a rest?

540
00:38:28,856 --> 00:38:30,936
Let's talk about it after he wakes up.

541
00:38:30,936 --> 00:38:32,716
It's also good to preserve his life.

542
00:38:34,356 --> 00:38:35,916
It's not that Su is unwilling.

543
00:38:36,636 --> 00:38:38,916
It's just
that official duties make it inconvenient.

544
00:38:40,196 --> 00:38:42,796
And I must advise madam
not to indulge in momentary compassion,

545
00:38:42,796 --> 00:38:43,996
thereby tolerating the demon.

546
00:38:44,956 --> 00:38:46,876
I just fear it may affect
Senior Official Pei's good reputation

547
00:38:46,876 --> 00:38:48,316
as well.

548
00:38:50,636 --> 00:38:52,716
Since you come here on orders
to take someone away,

549
00:38:53,316 --> 00:38:54,436
I shouldn't stand in the way.

550
00:38:55,636 --> 00:38:58,716
May I trouble you to show us
the official document to everyone?

551
00:39:03,916 --> 00:39:06,596
I was in a rush
when I left the house, so I did not bring it.

552
00:39:07,476 --> 00:39:09,876
Who doesn't know
that Master Mi is a notoriously wicked person?

553
00:39:10,556 --> 00:39:12,956
Could it be that you suspect
that I have wrongfully accused him?

554
00:39:12,956 --> 00:39:16,236
Not at all.it is not I that suspect you.

555
00:39:16,796 --> 00:39:19,796
Even if Mi has misconducted himself,
he has not yet been convicted.

556
00:39:19,796 --> 00:39:21,276
He is the people of Xizhou.

557
00:39:21,956 --> 00:39:25,236
Since you want to capture someone in Xizhou,
there must be some evidence.

558
00:39:25,876 --> 00:39:27,436
Although I am a woman,

559
00:39:27,436 --> 00:39:29,476
yet I cannot simply watch the people of Xizhou

560
00:39:29,476 --> 00:39:31,476
losing their lives
in such an unclear and unjust manner.

561
00:39:32,076 --> 00:39:34,076
Well, well. Nice speech.

562
00:39:34,076 --> 00:39:35,116
That's right indeed.

563
00:39:42,356 --> 00:39:45,396
Madam is determined
to obstruct my official duties.

564
00:39:45,396 --> 00:39:47,536
How dare I hinder your official business.

565
00:39:47,536 --> 00:39:50,036
Although it is official duty,
it has its own set of rules.

566
00:39:50,036 --> 00:39:51,596
Which state
would take people from another place

567
00:39:51,596 --> 00:39:53,356
without even a single official document?

568
00:39:53,956 --> 00:39:57,056
Does your honor think
that Xizhou is a county of Yizhou?

569
00:39:57,056 --> 00:40:00,196
As long as you want to take the initiative,
you can capture anyone you want.

570
00:40:00,196 --> 00:40:01,676
Can you capture whoever you want?

571
00:40:18,756 --> 00:40:20,716
This is the fish symbol of Chief Administrator.

572
00:40:21,516 --> 00:40:23,876
I wonder if this can be used as a credential?

573
00:40:29,028 --> 00:40:30,976
[Same as Commander]

574
00:40:34,396 --> 00:40:35,716
How much longer does the lady want to verify?

575
00:40:36,596 --> 00:40:38,396
Do you still suspect that Su is faking it?

576
00:40:40,556 --> 00:40:42,676
Of course, this symbol is genuine.

577
00:40:43,356 --> 00:40:46,396
So your father, Prefectural Governor Su,
has become the Chief Administrator.

578
00:40:46,396 --> 00:40:47,916
It deserves congratulation.

579
00:40:49,836 --> 00:40:51,576
Madam, what do you mean?

580
00:40:51,576 --> 00:40:53,956
Isn't Governor Su the Chief Administrator?

581
00:40:54,556 --> 00:40:56,956
Then why does this case of forcing good people
into servitude in Yizhou

582
00:40:56,956 --> 00:40:58,716
require the military command
of the Chief Administrator?

583
00:40:59,556 --> 00:41:00,608
Could it be that

584
00:41:00,608 --> 00:41:03,356
Mi forced someone
from the Chief Administrator's family

585
00:41:03,356 --> 00:41:04,636
to be scorned?

586
00:41:04,636 --> 00:41:06,236
Madam, please do not speak nonsense.

587
00:41:06,236 --> 00:41:08,296
How can you joke about Chief Administrator?

588
00:41:08,296 --> 00:41:11,556
Nonsense? Who just came in and spoke

589
00:41:11,556 --> 00:41:14,236
