and needs to be taken back for questioning?

590
00:41:14,236 --> 00:41:16,516
Who cannot produce the documents from Yizhou?

591
00:41:16,516 --> 00:41:18,436
But brought out a military token instead?

592
00:41:18,436 --> 00:41:20,716
Claim to arrest a merchant
who forces the good into servitude.

593
00:41:21,316 --> 00:41:22,416
But I didn't know this.

594
00:41:22,416 --> 00:41:26,076
I didn't realize that Commander would care
for the people of Xizhou like that.

595
00:41:26,076 --> 00:41:27,596
Even the merchants in the state and county

596
00:41:27,596 --> 00:41:29,596
and forcing good men to demon
should be inquired into.

597
00:41:30,396 --> 00:41:31,916
I am not unaware of what Mister Mi did.

598
00:41:31,916 --> 00:41:34,720
What on earth has he done
to enrage the Chief Administrator?

599
00:41:34,720 --> 00:41:35,796
So Master Su

600
00:41:35,796 --> 00:41:38,196
