regardless of his life.

601
00:41:38,916 --> 00:41:42,596
Or is it that so-called forcing a good man
is merely an excuse?

602
00:41:43,196 --> 00:41:46,756
Could it be that this Mi
hasn't truly succumbed to evil?

603
00:41:47,316 --> 00:41:49,956
But has witnessed something
he should not have seen?

604
00:41:49,956 --> 00:41:52,296
thus he must be silenced by death.

605
00:41:52,296 --> 00:41:55,516
Hold on, don't speak nonsense.

606
00:41:57,316 --> 00:42:00,436
Who said Chief Administrator
wants to arrest this person to kill him?

607
00:42:01,396 --> 00:42:04,376
So, it's not Chief Administrator
who wants to arrest people. It's okay.

608
00:42:04,376 --> 00:42:06,836
I have been hearing about murdering all day.

609
00:42:06,836 --> 00:42:08,436
And now you come here

610
00:42:08,436 --> 00:42:11,256
