to take him away.

611
00:42:11,256 --> 00:42:12,856
Therefore, I was a bit over-concerned.

612
00:42:12,856 --> 00:42:16,436
I am a woman, lacking insight,
I beg your pardon, Advisor.

613
00:42:18,276 --> 00:42:21,356
Since it's not Chief Administrator
wanting to arrest him, it makes it easier.

614
00:42:22,116 --> 00:42:24,396
